<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <Fragment slot="announcement"></Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="header">
    <Header
      links={[
        { text: "Home", href: "#" },
        { text: "About", href: "#about" },
        { text: "Resume", href: "#resume" },
        { text: "Porfolio", href: "#porfolio" },
        { text: "Blog", href: "#blog" },
        {
          text: "Github",
          href: "https://github.com/alexogeny",
        },
      ]}
      actions={[
        {
          text: "Follow",
          href: "https://x.com/alexogeny",
          target: "_blank",
          rel: "noopener noreferrer",
        },
      ]}
      isSticky
      showToggleTheme
    />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero2 Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero
    id="hero"
    title="Alex Mack"
    tagline="Code can save the world."
    actions={[
      // { variant: "primary", target: "_blank", text: "Hire me", href: "/" },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      I'm passionate about coding and love creating stuff that actually works.<br
      />
       I love building stuff that makes a difference and challenges my skills. I
      love to learn and I love to teach.
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    id="about"
    columns={3}
    items={[
      {
        icon: "tabler:brand-x",
        callToAction: {
          target: "_blank",
          text: "Twitter",
          href: "https://x.com/alexogeny",
        },
      },
      {
        icon: "tabler:brand-github",
        callToAction: {
          target: "_blank",
          text: "Github",
          href: "https://github.com/alexogeny",
        },
      },
      {
        icon: "tabler:brand-discord",
        callToAction: {
          target: "_blank",
          text: "Discord",
          href: "https://discord.com/users/305879281580638228",
        },
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6896115",
      alt: "alexogeny's picture",
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2"
      >
        Hey
      </h3>
      <p>
        Welcome to my distinctive realm of creativity, where I don't just write
        code—I craft experiences. Consider each pixel a stroke of my digital
        paintbrush, intricately used to weave compelling visual narratives that
        don't just catch the eye, but captivate the soul.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        My interests are as diverse as my skill set. A trinity of coding,
        gaming, and music fuels my creativity. I'm also an aficionado of the
        great outdoors, continually finding inspiration in the world's natural
        beauty. Storytelling, in any form, captivates me—be it through the pages
        of a gripping novel or the scenes of a riveting show.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>Wanna see more of what I'm up to? Hit that follow:</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

